  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The Committee For The Purchase From People Who Are Blind Or Severely Disabled operates a program under 41 U.S.C. 8504 for supplying items to Government contracts.&lt;SEP&gt;This committee operates a program under 41 U.S.C. 8504 requiring certain supplies from nonprofit agencies.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6266f048b10bdb8222f03b8f5e597d7e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4bcb91b404a9ca74c18944c1ba7f80a2</data>
