  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">The Site Visit is tentatively scheduled for 23-25 September 2025, with government-provided transportation and strict security protocols.&lt;SEP&gt;The site visit is tentatively scheduled for 23-25 September 2025 at NAS Jacksonville, with transportation provided and special security instructions.</data>
