  <data key="d2">Standard Form 33 must be completed and signed with UEI number and CAGE code for the responsibility determination.&lt;SEP&gt;Standard Form 33 is the form used for the solicitation, offer, and award, prescribed by GSA under FAR 48 CFR 53.214(c), revised 6/2014.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-f8cbd3bc2ef4445a2ce77064100a7a3e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6266f048b10bdb8222f03b8f5e597d7e</data>
