<node id="System For Award Management">
  <data key="d0">System For Award Management</data>
  <data key="d1">technology</data>
  <data key="d2">The System For Award Management is referenced for representations and certifications under FAR 52.204-7.&lt;SEP&gt;The System for Award Management is an electronic database accessed via https://www.sam.gov for completing annual representations and certifications.&lt;SEP&gt;The System for Award Management is used for maintenance, reporting executive compensation, incorporation of representations, and electronic funds transfer payments under various FAR clauses.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6266f048b10bdb8222f03b8f5e597d7e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4bcb91b404a9ca74c18944c1ba7f80a2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-96e30762ee04dbe2af303802d3d2a936</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759711345</data>
</node>
