  <data key="d0">Price Proposal Binder</data>
  <data key="d1">document</data>
  <data key="d2">The Price Proposal Binder requires two copies including pricing data, ELIN spreadsheet, and electronic formats on CD.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6266f048b10bdb8222f03b8f5e597d7e</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759711345</data>
</node>
<node id="Non-Price Proposal Binder">
  <data key="d0">Non-Price Proposal Binder</data>
  <data key="d1">document</data>
  <data key="d2">The Non-Price Proposal Binder requires three copies including non-price factors, with a 150-page limit and electronic formats on CD.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6266f048b10bdb8222f03b8f5e597d7e</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759711345</data>
</node>
<node id="L.14 Small Business Subcontracting Plan">
  <data key="d0">L.14 Small Business Subcontracting Plan</data>
  <data key="d1">section</data>
  <data key="d2">L.14 Small Business Subcontracting Plan requires other than small businesses to submit an SBSP using Attachment JL-8 template, with NAVFAC targets.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6266f048b10bdb8222f03b8f5e597d7e</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759711345</data>
</node>
<node id="Small Business Subcontracting Plan">
  <data key="d0">Small Business Subcontracting Plan</data>
  <data key="d1">requirement</data>
  <data key="d2">The Small Business Subcontracting Plan must be submitted by other than small businesses, negotiated for acceptability, and incorporated into the contract.&lt;SEP&gt;The Small Business Subcontracting Plan is required under FAR 52.219-9 and DFARS 252.219-7003, with liquidated damages for noncompliance under FAR 52.219-16.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6266f048b10bdb8222f03b8f5e597d7e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-96e30762ee04dbe2af303802d3d2a936</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759711345</data>
</node>
<node id="NAVFAC">
  <data key="d0">NAVFAC</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">NAVFAC is the organization maintaining the Contractor Incident Reporting System for safety data.&lt;SEP&gt;NAVFAC is an organization that utilizes Maximo data for government planning, programming, and budgeting processes.&lt;SEP&gt;NAVFAC establishes command-wide small business subcontracting targets based on a percentage of total planned subcontract dollars.&lt;SEP&gt;NAVFAC provides command-wide small business subcontracting targets including 40% for Small Business and others.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6277b393cb9cf1d4f0f247c35b0fffa1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6266f048b10bdb8222f03b8f5e597d7e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9775b66c35e6cfe40c05dbf72803d6cd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b1019473eb9ce96e37dbd7a39cfdf02d</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759711345</data>
</node>
<node id="Attachment JL-8">
  <data key="d0">Attachment JL-8</data>
  <data key="d1">document</data>
  <data key="d2">Attachment JL-8 is the template for the Small Business Subcontracting Plan.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6266f048b10bdb8222f03b8f5e597d7e</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759711345</data>
</node>
<node id="41 U.S.C. 8504">
  <data key="d0">41 U.S.C. 8504</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">41 U.S.C. 8504 is the legal authority for the program operated by the Committee for the Purchase from People Who Are Blind or Severely Disabled.&lt;SEP&gt;This U.S. Code section authorizes the program operated by the Committee for purchases from nonprofit agencies employing people who are blind or severely disabled.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6266f048b10bdb8222f03b8f5e597d7e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4bcb91b404a9ca74c18944c1ba7f80a2</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759711345</data>
</node>
<node id="Government Pre-Award Inquiry Form">
  <data key="d0">Government Pre-Award Inquiry Form</data>
  <data key="d1">document</data>
  <data key="d2">The Government Pre-Award Inquiry Form is provided as Attachment JL-2 for submitting questions in writing.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6266f048b10bdb8222f03b8f5e597d7e</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759711345</data>
</node>
