  <data key="d0">Attachment JL-1</data>
  <data key="d1">document</data>
  <data key="d2">Attachment JL-1 is a Microsoft Excel version required for total effort including prime contractor and subcontractors for the base period.&lt;SEP&gt;Attachment JL-1 is a staffing levels spreadsheet provided as N6945025R0003_JL1_Labor_Hours_Hours_Spreadsheet.xlsx, required for submission in Excel format with basis of estimate rationale.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ac133babc8ecde7c6f7014a40f53ce13&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b1019473eb9ce96e37dbd7a39cfdf02d</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759711346</data>
