  <data key="d0">Fully Loaded Pricing</data>
  <data key="d1">requirement</data>
  <data key="d2">All pricing must be fully loaded, including recurring and non-recurring elements, with no additional fees or allocations applied upon option exercise.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4bcb91b404a9ca74c18944c1ba7f80a2</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759711353</data>
