  <data key="d0">Port Operations (0600000)</data>
  <data key="d1">requirement</data>
  <data key="d2">Port Operations (0600000) is a technical annex requiring services similar to those in the RFP for demonstrating relevant experience.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ac133babc8ecde7c6f7014a40f53ce13</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759711353</data>
</node>
<node id="Facility Investment (1502000)">
  <data key="d0">Facility Investment (1502000)</data>
  <data key="d1">requirement</data>
  <data key="d2">Facility Investment (1502000) includes completion of service orders, HVAC Systems maintenance and repairs, Fire Protection Systems maintenance and repairs, and two other facility investment items as specified in the RFP.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ac133babc8ecde7c6f7014a40f53ce13</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759711353</data>
</node>
<node id="Electrical (1602000)">
  <data key="d0">Electrical (1602000)</data>
  <data key="d1">requirement</data>
  <data key="d2">Electrical (1602000) covers Transmission and Distribution operations, maintenance, and repairs similar to RFP requirements.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ac133babc8ecde7c6f7014a40f53ce13</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759711353</data>
</node>
<node id="Water (1606000)">
  <data key="d0">Water (1606000)</data>
  <data key="d1">requirement</data>
  <data key="d2">Water (1606000) includes Raw Water Supply, Water Treatment Plant and Distribution System operation, Laboratory and Testing processes, maintenance, and repairs similar to RFP requirements.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ac133babc8ecde7c6f7014a40f53ce13</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759711353</data>
</node>
<node id="BSVE (1700000)">
  <data key="d0">BSVE (1700000)</data>
  <data key="d1">requirement</data>
  <data key="d2">BSVE (1700000) involves operations, maintenance, and repair of Civil Engineering Support Equipment (CESE) and Weight Handling Equipment (WHE) similar to RFP requirements.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ac133babc8ecde7c6f7014a40f53ce13</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759711353</data>
</node>
<node id="Management Approach">
  <data key="d0">Management Approach</data>
  <data key="d1">evaluation_factor</data>
  <data key="d2">Management Approach is Factor 2, evaluated for feasibility in controlling the project, including workforce management, quality management system, scheduling, and phase-in plans.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ac133babc8ecde7c6f7014a40f53ce13</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759711353</data>
</node>
<node id="Technical Approach">
  <data key="d0">Technical Approach</data>
  <data key="d1">evaluation_factor</data>
  <data key="d2">Technical Approach is Factor 3, requiring description of methodologies for annexes and sub-annexes, including staffing levels, performance objectives, and systems approach.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ac133babc8ecde7c6f7014a40f53ce13</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759711353</data>
</node>
<node id="Attachment JM-1">
  <data key="d0">Attachment JM-1</data>
  <data key="d1">document</data>
  <data key="d2">Attachment JM-1 is the Corporate Experience Project Data Sheet used for submitting project examples, expandable beyond two pages.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ac133babc8ecde7c6f7014a40f53ce13</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759711353</data>
</node>
<node id="Joint Venture (JV)">
  <data key="d0">Joint Venture (JV)</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">A Joint Venture (JV) allows submission of experience from the JV entity or partners, limited to five projects total, with requirements for demonstrating portions of work performed by proposing partners.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ac133babc8ecde7c6f7014a40f53ce13</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759711353</data>
</node>
<node id="Mentor-Protege Agreements">
  <data key="d0">Mentor-Protege Agreements</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Mentor-Protege Agreements approved by the Small Business Administration exempt certain JV requirements for demonstrating prime contractor experience.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ac133babc8ecde7c6f7014a40f53ce13</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759711353</data>
</node>
<node id="Quality Management System (QMS)">
  <data key="d0">Quality Management System (QMS)</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Quality Management System (QMS) is a program ensuring compliance with management and administration requirements, including processes for quality control oversight and performance measurement.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ac133babc8ecde7c6f7014a40f53ce13</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759711353</data>
</node>
<node id="Performance Work Statement (PWS)">
  <data key="d0">Performance Work Statement (PWS)</data>
  <data key="d1">document</data>
  <data key="d2">The Performance Work Statement (PWS) describes the scope of services, including annexes and sub-annexes, used to define relevant project similarities.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ac133babc8ecde7c6f7014a40f53ce13</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759711353</data>
</node>
<node id="Basis of Estimate (BOE)">
  <data key="d0">Basis of Estimate (BOE)</data>
  <data key="d1">deliverable</data>
  <data key="d2">Basis of Estimate (BOE) includes labor classification, annual direct and indirect labor hours, data sources, and methodology for each specification item in Attachment JL-1.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ac133babc8ecde7c6f7014a40f53ce13</data>
