  <data key="d0">Small Business Administration</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Maintains the List of Qualified HUBZone Small Business Concerns, determines affiliation under 13 CFR 121.103, and sets size standards at sba.gov.&lt;SEP&gt;The Small Business Administration approves Mentor-Protege Agreements that provide exemptions for certain Joint Venture experience requirements in corporate experience evaluation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-bafeb026eba657c5147474a89dc0e6f9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ac133babc8ecde7c6f7014a40f53ce13</data>
